{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Shopify Developer Prompt – Animated Storytelling Character Section
    
    I need you to create an interactive storytelling section similar to the About page here:
    
    https://www.forhers.com/about
    
    The goal is to recreate a modern animated hero section with a centered character and animated text around it.
    
    This is NOT a normal content section.
    It must replicate the visual storytelling animation style of the reference.
    
    1. Core Concept
    
    The section should display:
    
    A large character illustration positioned in the center
    
    Animated text appearing around or near the character
    
    Text that changes or animates as the user scrolls
    
    The section should feel like a visual story introduction, not a static block of text.
    
    2. Character Placement
    
    The character image must:
    
    Be perfectly centered horizontally
    
    Slightly above vertical center of the screen
    
    Be the visual focus of the section
    
    Requirements:
    
    Uploadable character image
    
    Adjustable size
    
    Optional floating animation
    
    Settings required in Shopify editor:
    
    Character image upload
    
    Character width control
    
    Character vertical position
    
    Character animation toggle
    
    Character animation speed
    
    3. Animated Text Effect
    
    Text should appear with modern animation effects.
    
    Examples of acceptable animations:
    
    Fade + slide in
    
    Typewriter effect
    
    Character-by-character reveal
    
    Word-by-word reveal
    
    Scroll-triggered transitions
    
    Text should animate dynamically when the user scrolls.
    
    The animation must feel premium and smooth like the reference site.
    
    Animated text is usually created with CSS keyframe animations or JavaScript scroll triggers.
    
    4. Text Positioning
    
    Text can appear:
    
    Left of the character
    
    Right of the character
    
    Above the character
    
    Below the character
    
    Allow positioning options inside Shopify editor.
    
    Controls required:
    
    Text alignment
    
    Text position
    
    Maximum width
    
    Spacing from character
    
    5. Scroll Interaction
    
    The section should support scroll-based animation.
    
    Examples:
    
    When user scrolls:
    
    New text appears
    
    Text fades out and new text fades in
    
    Character slightly moves or floats
    
    Content changes smoothly
    
    This creates the storytelling experience like the reference page.
    
    6. Background Customization
    
    The entire section background must be fully customizable.
    
    The Shopify editor must allow choosing:
    
    Solid Color
    
    Color picker.
    
    Gradient Background
    
    Two color pickers.
    
    Image Background
    
    Upload custom image.
    
    Additional controls:
    
    Background image position
    
    Background size (cover / contain)
    
    Overlay color
    
    Overlay opacity
    
    7. Typography Controls
    
    Allow full typography customization.
    
    Controls required:
    
    Title
    
    Font family
    
    Font size
    
    Font weight
    
    Color
    
    Body Text
    
    Font family
    
    Font size
    
    Color
    
    Line height
    
    Letter spacing
    
    8. Section Height
    
    The section should behave like a full screen hero area.
    
    Options:
    
    100vh full screen
    
    Adjustable height
    
    9. Responsiveness
    
    The section must be responsive across all devices.
    
    Supported devices:
    
    Mobile phones
    
    Tablets
    
    Laptops
    
    Desktop monitors
    
    Ultra-wide screens
    
    Smart TVs
    
    Desktop Layout
    
    Character centered
    Text appears around it.
    
    Tablet Layout
    
    Character slightly smaller
    Text stacked around it.
    
    Mobile Layout
    
    Character on top
    Text below
    
    Animations must remain smooth.
    
    10. Shopify Customization
    
    Inside Shopify Theme Editor I must be able to:
    
    Upload the character image
    
    Edit animated texts
    
    Add multiple text steps
    
    Adjust text positions
    
    Change fonts
    
    Change colors
    
    Change background
    
    Adjust animation speed
    
    Toggle animations on/off
    
    11. Performance
    
    The animation must be lightweight.
    
    Requirements:
    
    CSS animations when possible
    
    Minimal JavaScript
    
    Smooth scrolling
    
    Optimized images
    
    12. Code Requirements
    
    Implementation must follow Shopify standards:
    
    Build as Shopify section (.liquid)
    
    Use schema settings for customization
    
    Clean modular code
    
    Compatible with Online Store 2.0
    
    Final Goal
    
    Create a modern animated storytelling section where:
    
    A character stands in the middle
    
    Text animates around it
    
    The section feels alive and interactive
    
    Everything is customizable from the Shopify theme editor
    
    Works perfectly on all devices, make the animations look better, make me able to customize background with either gradient color or picture or normal color , make me able to remove boxes or add boxes , make me able to change font and picture size , make it extremely responsive on all devices
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-storytelling-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: {{ block.settings.section_height }}vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    overflow-y: visible;
    {% if block.settings.background_type == 'color' %}
      background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    {% elsif block.settings.background_type == 'gradient' %}
      background: linear-gradient({{ block.settings.gradient_angle }}deg, {{ block.settings.gradient_color_1 }} 0%, {{ block.settings.gradient_color_2 }} 100%);
    {% elsif block.settings.background_type == 'image' and block.settings.background_image %}
      background-image: url('{{ block.settings.background_image | image_url: width: 2000 }}');
      background-size: {{ block.settings.background_size }};
      background-position: {{ block.settings.background_position }};
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-storytelling-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.overlay_color }};
    opacity: {{ block.settings.overlay_opacity | divided_by: 100.0 }};
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ai-storytelling-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: {{ block.settings.section_height }}vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }

  .ai-storytelling-character-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: {{ block.settings.character_width }}%;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    {% if block.settings.character_float_animation %}
      animation: ai-storytelling-float-{{ ai_gen_id }} {{ block.settings.character_animation_speed }}s ease-in-out infinite;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-storytelling-character-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .ai-storytelling-character-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-storytelling-character-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 60%;
    height: 60%;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .ai-storytelling-text-box-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 3;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
    max-width: {{ block.settings.text_max_width }}px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.text_box_padding }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.text_box_bg_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.text_box_radius }}px;
    {% if block.settings.text_box_shadow %}
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-storytelling-text-box-{{ ai_gen_id }}.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .ai-storytelling-text-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.title_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.title_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.title_font.weight }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_font_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color }};
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-storytelling-text-body-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.body_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.body_font.weight }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.body_font_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.body_color }};
    line-height: {{ block.settings.body_line_height }};
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.body_letter_spacing }}px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  {% if block.settings.character_float_animation %}
    @keyframes ai-storytelling-float-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translateY(0px);
      }
      50% {
        transform: translateY(-20px);
      }
    }
  {% endif %}

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-storytelling-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      min-height: auto;
      height: auto;
      overflow-y: visible;
    }

    .ai-storytelling-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: auto;
      height: auto;
      align-items: stretch;
      padding: 30px 15px;
    }

    .ai-storytelling-character-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      max-width: {{ block.settings.character_width_mobile }}%;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .ai-storytelling-text-box-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .ai-storytelling-text-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.title_font_size | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }

    .ai-storytelling-text-body-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.body_font_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-storytelling-text-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.title_font_size | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }

    .ai-storytelling-text-body-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.body_font_size | times: 0.85 }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<animated-storytelling-{{ ai_gen_id }}
  class="ai-storytelling-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
  data-scroll-trigger="{{ block.settings.scroll_trigger }}"
  data-animation-type="{{ block.settings.animation_type }}"
  {{ block.shopify_attributes }}
>
  {% if block.settings.background_type != 'color' or block.settings.overlay_opacity > 0 %}
    <div class="ai-storytelling-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
  {% endif %}

  <div class="ai-storytelling-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-storytelling-character-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.character_image %}
        <img
          src="{{ block.settings.character_image | image_url: width: 1200 }}"
          alt="{{ block.settings.character_image.alt | escape }}"
          class="ai-storytelling-character-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          loading="lazy"
          width="{{ block.settings.character_image.width }}"
          height="{{ block.settings.character_image.height }}"
        >
      {% else %}
        <div class="ai-storytelling-character-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    {% for i in (1..6) %}
      {% liquid
        assign text_enabled_key = 'text_' | append: i | append: '_enabled'
        assign text_title_key = 'text_' | append: i | append: '_title'
        assign text_body_key = 'text_' | append: i | append: '_body'
        assign text_position_key = 'text_' | append: i | append: '_position'
        assign text_offset_x_key = 'text_' | append: i | append: '_offset_x'
        assign text_offset_y_key = 'text_' | append: i | append: '_offset_y'
        assign text_delay_key = 'text_' | append: i | append: '_delay'

        assign text_enabled = block.settings[text_enabled_key]
        assign text_title = block.settings[text_title_key]
        assign text_body = block.settings[text_body_key]
        assign text_position = block.settings[text_position_key]
        assign text_offset_x = block.settings[text_offset_x_key]
        assign text_offset_y = block.settings[text_offset_y_key]
        assign text_delay = block.settings[text_delay_key]
      %}

      {% if text_enabled %}
        <div
          class="ai-storytelling-text-box-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          data-position="{{ text_position }}"
          data-offset-x="{{ text_offset_x }}"
          data-offset-y="{{ text_offset_y }}"
          data-delay="{{ text_delay }}"
          style="
            {% if text_position == 'top-left' %}
              top: {{ text_offset_y }}%;
              left: {{ text_offset_x }}%;
            {% elsif text_position == 'top-right' %}
              top: {{ text_offset_y }}%;
              right: {{ text_offset_x }}%;
            {% elsif text_position == 'bottom-left' %}
              bottom: {{ text_offset_y }}%;
              left: {{ text_offset_x }}%;
            {% elsif text_position == 'bottom-right' %}
              bottom: {{ text_offset_y }}%;
              right: {{ text_offset_x }}%;
            {% elsif text_position == 'center-left' %}
              top: 50%;
              left: {{ text_offset_x }}%;
              transform: translateY(-50%);
            {% elsif text_position == 'center-right' %}
              top: 50%;
              right: {{ text_offset_x }}%;
              transform: translateY(-50%);
            {% endif %}
            transition-delay: {{ text_delay | divided_by: 1000.0 }}s;
          "
        >
          {% if text_title != blank %}
            <h3 class="ai-storytelling-text-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ text_title }}</h3>
          {% endif %}
          {% if text_body != blank %}
            <div class="ai-storytelling-text-body-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ text_body }}</div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</animated-storytelling-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class AnimatedStorytelling{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
        this.textBoxes = [];
        this.observer = null;
        this.scrollTrigger = this.dataset.scrollTrigger === 'true';
        this.animationType = this.dataset.animationType || 'fade';
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.textBoxes = Array.from(this.querySelectorAll('.ai-storytelling-text-box-{{ ai_gen_id }}'));
        
        if (this.scrollTrigger) {
          this.setupScrollObserver();
        } else {
          this.animateSequentially();
        }

        this.repositionTextBoxesMobile();
        window.addEventListener('resize', () => this.repositionTextBoxesMobile());
      }

      setupScrollObserver() {
        const options = {
          root: null,
          rootMargin: '0px',
          threshold: 0.3
        };

        this.observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
          entries.forEach(entry => {
            if (entry.isIntersecting) {
              this.animateSequentially();
              this.observer.unobserve(entry.target);
            }
          });
        }, options);

        this.observer.observe(this);
      }

      animateSequentially() {
        this.textBoxes.forEach((box, index) => {
          const delay = parseInt(box.dataset.delay) || index * 300;
          setTimeout(() => {
            box.classList.add('visible');
          }, delay);
        });
      }

      repositionTextBoxesMobile() {
        if (window.innerWidth <= 989) {
          this.textBoxes.forEach((box) => {
            box.style.position = 'relative';
            box.style.top = 'auto';
            box.style.left = 'auto';
            box.style.right = 'auto';
            box.style.bottom = 'auto';
            box.style.transform = 'none';
          });
        } else {
          this.textBoxes.forEach((box) => {
            const position = box.dataset.position;
            const offsetX = box.dataset.offsetX;
            const offsetY = box.dataset.offsetY;
            
            box.style.position = 'absolute';
            
            if (position === 'top-left') {
              box.style.top = offsetY + '%';
              box.style.left = offsetX + '%';
            } else if (position === 'top-right') {
              box.style.top = offsetY + '%';
              box.style.right = offsetX + '%';
            } else if (position === 'bottom-left') {
              box.style.bottom = offsetY + '%';
              box.style.left = offsetX + '%';
            } else if (position === 'bottom-right') {
              box.style.bottom = offsetY + '%';
              box.style.right = offsetX + '%';
            } else if (position === 'center-left') {
              box.style.top = '50%';
              box.style.left = offsetX + '%';
              box.style.transform = 'translateY(-50%)';
            } else if (position === 'center-right') {
              box.style.top = '50%';
              box.style.right = offsetX + '%';
              box.style.transform = 'translateY(-50%)';
            }
          });
        }
      }

      disconnectedCallback() {
        if (this.observer) {
          this.observer.disconnect();
        }
        window.removeEventListener('resize', () => this.repositionTextBoxesMobile());
      }
    }

    customElements.define('animated-storytelling-{{ ai_gen_id }}', AnimatedStorytelling{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

